NEW TUTORIAL_GOVERNMENTVIEW_GOVERNMENT_DESC:1 "The §SGovernment§! screen presents us with information regarding our empire and its government. Here we can see our §SRuler§! and any related effects.\n\nA separate tab gives information on the §SDemographics§! of our empire."
OLD TUTORIAL_GOVERNMENTVIEW_GOVERNMENT_DESC:0 "The §SGovernment§! screen presents us with information regarding our empire and its government. Here we can see our §SRuler§! and any related effects.\n\nSeparate tabs give a detailed overview of our §SBudget§! and information on the §SDemographics§! of our nation."
CHANGE TUTORIAL_GOVERNMENTVIEW_GOVERNMENT_DESC:1 "§S政府§!界面显示了关于我帝国和帝国政府的信息。在这里可以看到我们的§S统治者§!和相关效果。\n\n另一个标签提供了帝国§S人口统计§!数据的概览。"
CN2 TUTORIAL_GOVERNMENTVIEW_GOVERNMENT_DESC:1 "§S政府§!界面显示了关于我们帝国及其政府的有关信息。在这里可以看到我们的§S统治者§!以及相关的效果。\n\n另一个界面显示了我们帝国的§S人口统计§!数据。"
NEW TUTORIAL_EMPIREVIEW_PLANETS_DESC:4 "The §SPlanets and Sectors§! screen provides an overview of all our colonized worlds, their §SPops§!, and their §SResource Output§!. As our empire grows it will be automatically organized into §SSectors§!, which are vital to administering larger empires.\n\n§SSectors§! can be given resources and told to automatically build and upgrade §SBuildings§! and §SDistricts§! on their planets."
OLD TUTORIAL_EMPIREVIEW_PLANETS_DESC:2 "The §SPlanets and Sectors§! screen provides an overview of all our colonized worlds, their §SPops§!, and §SResource Output§!. It also allows us to create and manage semi-autonomous §SSectors§!, which are vital to administering larger empires."
CHANGE TUTORIAL_EMPIREVIEW_PLANETS_DESC:4 "§S行星和星域!界面显示了我们所有殖民星球的概览，包括其§人口§!和§S资源产出§!。随着帝国的发展，星球将自动组成§S星域§!，星域对于管理庞大的帝国至关重要。\n\n你可以为§S星域§!分配资源，并设置自动建造并升级行星上的§S建筑§!和§S地区§!。"
CN2 TUTORIAL_EMPIREVIEW_PLANETS_DESC:4 "§S星球与星域§!界面提供了我们所有殖民星球的概览，其§S人口§!，以及§S资源产出§!。随着帝国的发展，星球将自动组成§S星域§!，这对管理庞大的帝国来说至关重要。\n\n你可以为§S星域§!分配资源，并设置自动建造和升级星球上的§S建筑§!与§S区划§!。"
NEW TUTORIAL_PLANETVIEW_PLANET_DESC:2 "This is our homeworld and the §SCapital§! of our empire. The §SPlanet Summary§! screen, which we are currently looking at, provides an overview of the planet's important statistics.\n\nWe can see the total number of §SDistricts§! this planet can support, how many §SPops§! are living on it, and how much §SFood§! and other §SResources§! it produces and consumes. We can also see if the planet is suffering from low §SStability§!, and if there is an assigned §SGovernor§!, they are found here."
OLD TUTORIAL_PLANETVIEW_PLANET_DESC:0 "This is our homeworld and the §SCapital§! of our empire. The §SPlanet Summary§! screen, which we are currently looking at, provides an overview of the planet's important statistics.\n\nAmong other things, we can see the total number of §STiles§! this planet has, how many §SPops§! are living on it and how much §SFood§! it produces. We can also see if the planet is suffering from §SUnrest§!, and if there is an assigned §SGovernor§!, they are found here."
CHANGE TUTORIAL_PLANETVIEW_PLANET_DESC:2 "这是我们的母星，也是帝国的§S首都§!。我们现在看到的§S行星总览§!界面，显示了这颗行星的重要数据概览。\n\n我们可以看到这颗行星可以支持的§S地区§!总数，上面生活的§S人口§!数和行星生产消耗的§S食物§!及其它§S资源§!数量。我们也可以看到这颗行星的§S稳定度§!是否过低。而且如果指派了§S总督§!，也会显示在这里。"
CN2 TUTORIAL_PLANETVIEW_PLANET_DESC:2 "这是我们的母星，也是帝国的§S首都§!。我们目前正在浏览的是§S星球总览§!界面，显示了星球的重要统计数据。\n\n我们可以看到这颗星球可以支持的§S区划§!总数，上面住着多少§S人口§!，以及生产和消耗多少§S食物§!与其它§S资源§!。我们也可以看到这颗星球的§S稳定性§!是否过低，而且如果指派了§S总督§!，也会显示在这里。"
NEW TUTORIAL_PLANETVIEW_TILES_TITLE:1 "Population View"
OLD TUTORIAL_PLANETVIEW_TILES_TITLE:0 "Surface View"
CHANGE TUTORIAL_PLANETVIEW_TILES_TITLE:1 "人口界面"
CN2 TUTORIAL_PLANETVIEW_TILES_TITLE:1 "人口界面"
NEW TUTORIAL_PLANETVIEW_TILES_DESC:2 "Here we see a breakdown of this planet's population, divided into layers, or §SStrata§!.\n\nThey can be expanded to view the §SJob§! types within each §SStratum§!. §SJobs§! use and produce different resources, and the Pop working a Job needs a certain amount of §SHousing§! and §SAmenities§!. A lack of either will reduce §SHappiness§!, which can lower the planet's §SStability§!."
OLD TUTORIAL_PLANETVIEW_TILES_DESC:0 "Here we see a visual representation of this planet's surface, divided into §STiles§!. This tab is only visible on colonies and surveyed worlds that are habitable. Each §SPop§! occupies a single tile, which means that there can never be more Pops on a planet than there are free tiles.\n\nIn addition to a Pop, a §STile§! can also support a §SBuilding§!. To get the most out of a planet, we will need to carefully manage our §SPops§!, §SBuildings§! and §STiles§!."
CN  TUTORIAL_PLANETVIEW_TILES_DESC:2 "在这个标签页。可以看到行星的地块情况。只有在已殖民的行星或者勘察过的可居住行星上才可看到此标签页。每个§S人口§!都会占据一个地块，一个行星上的人口数不能超过可用的地块数。\n\n除了人口之外，§S地块§!上还能建造§S建筑§!。要获得行星的最大产出，必须精细管理行星的§S人口§!，§S建筑§!和§S地块§!。"
CN2 TUTORIAL_PLANETVIEW_TILES_DESC:2 "这里我们可以看到星球的人口明细，分划为不同的层次，或者叫§S阶层§!。\n\n我们可以展开§S社会阶层§!来查看里面的§S职位§!类型。§S职位§!使用并生产各种资源，而且从事职位的人口需要一定数量的§S住房§!和§S舒适度§!。如果任一需求未能得到满足，就会降低§S幸福度§!，导致星球的§S稳定性§!下降。"
NEW TUTORIAL_PLANETVIEW_COMBAT_DESC:4 "This is where we manage all ground forces on this planet. This screen also tracks how much §SDevastation§!, or damage, the planet itself has suffered.\n\nNew §SArmies§! are also raised here, by clicking the §SRecruit§! button in the center. §SDefense Armies§! are produced automatically by §SPops§! working Enforcer or Soldier §SJobs§!. These jobs are provided by the planetary capital, £building£ §SPrecinct Houses§!, and £building£ §SStrongholds§!."
OLD TUTORIAL_PLANETVIEW_COMBAT_DESC:2 "This is where we manage all ground forces on this planet. The upper portion of this view is divided into three sections. The top section represents the orbital space above the planet, the middle section is the atmosphere and the bottom section is the surface.\n\nNew §SArmies§! are also raised here, by clicking §SRecruit§! in the bottom right. A limited number of §SDefense Armies§! are produced automatically by your planetary capital building as well as any additional §SStronghold§! buildings that are present and manned by a §SPop§!."
CN  TUTORIAL_PLANETVIEW_COMBAT_DESC:4 "在这里，可以对行星上的所有地面单位进行管理。界面上方分为三个部分，最上部分为行星上方的轨道空间，中间部分为大气层，而最下部分为行星表面。\n\n单击右下方的§S招募§!按键，就可以招募新的§S部队§!。你的行星首府以及§S要塞§!等建筑会按照§S人口§!自动产生一定数量的§S防御部队§!。"
CN2 TUTORIAL_PLANETVIEW_COMBAT_DESC:4 "我们可以在这里管理星球上的所有地面部队。这一界面也显示星球遭受的§S破坏§!程度，也就是受到了多少伤害。\n\n点击中央的§S招募§!按钮，可以招募新的§S军团§!。§S防御军团§!由从事§S职位§!为执法者或是士兵的§S人口§!自动生产。这些职位由星球首都，£building£ §S警署§!，以及£building£ §S要塞§!提供。"
