NEW TUTORIAL_GOVERNMENTVIEW_DECISIONS_DESC:3 "Here empire-wide §SEdicts§!, practices that can be enforced by spending some of our resources, can be enacted."
OLD TUTORIAL_GOVERNMENTVIEW_DECISIONS_DESC:2 "The §SPolicies§! tab covers government §SPolicies§! as well as empire-wide §SEdicts§!, practices that can be enforced by spending some of our resources.\n\nThere are often a few possible stances to take for any given §SPolicy§!, though we may be limited by technology as well as our §SEthos§!."
CN  TUTORIAL_GOVERNMENTVIEW_DECISIONS_DESC:3 "§S政策§!标签页显示的是政府§S政策§!以及帝国§S法令§!，可以通过花费一些我们的资源来实施。\n\n对于任何§S政策§!，都会产生若干种相应影响，但某些态度可能会受到科技以及§S特征§!的限制。"
CN2 TUTORIAL_GOVERNMENTVIEW_DECISIONS_DESC:3 "我们可以在这里颁布帝国§S法令§!，即通过花费一些资源来实施的规定，其效果影响整个帝国。"
NEW TUTORIAL_EMPIREVIEW_FACTIONS_DESC:3 "The §SFactions§! screen gives an overview of the populace's political leanings. Be aware that shifts in the sociopolitical climate may give rise to §SFactions§!. Details on §SFaction§! sizes, attractiveness to our Pops, and how content they are may also be found here.\n\n§SFactions§! have §SIssues§! that are important to their overall §SApproval§!, and our policies and actions as a nation may displease or please these groupings, providing an increasing boost to £influence£ §SInfluence§! generation. The strength of §SFactions§! and the nature of their §SIssues§! can change along with our circumstances, but keep in mind that the §SHappiness§! of a §SPop§! can be affected by the §SApproval§! of the §SFaction§! it belongs to.\n\nWe can also §SManage Factions§! to manipulate the relationship between a §SFaction§! and the state, even going so far as embracing the ethos of a strong §SFaction§!."
OLD TUTORIAL_EMPIREVIEW_FACTIONS_DESC:1 "The §SFactions§! screen gives an overview of the populace's political leanings. Be aware that shifts in the sociopolitical climate may give rise to §SFactions§!. Details on §SFaction§! sizes, attractiveness to our Pops, and how content they are may also be found here.\n\n§SFactions§! have §SIssues§! that are important to their overall §SHappiness§!, and our policies and actions as a nation may displease or please these groupings, potentially providing a boost to £influence §SInfluence§! generation. The strength of §SFactions§! and the nature of their §SIssues§! can change along with our circumstances, but keep in mind that the §SBase Happiness§! of a §SPop§! is determined by the §SHappiness§! of the §SFaction§! it belongs to.\n\nWe can also §SManage Factions§! to manipulate the relationship between a §SFaction§! and the state, even going so far as embracing the ethos of a strong §SFaction§!."
CN  TUTORIAL_EMPIREVIEW_FACTIONS_DESC:3 "§S党派§!标签页显示人口的政治团体，可以让我们知道他们的§S诉求§!，与他们进行交流。"
CN2 TUTORIAL_EMPIREVIEW_FACTIONS_DESC:3 "§S派系§!界面显示了人口政治倾向的概览。注意社会政治气氛的变化可能会产生新的§S派系§!。这里也显示了§S派系§!规模，对我们人口的吸引力，以及派系满意程度的细节。\n\n§S派系§!有自己的§S诉求§!，这对他们的§S赞同度§!有着很大的影响，而我们国家的政策与行动可能会惹恼或取悦这些团体，增加£influence£ §S影响力§!的产出。§S派系§!的实力与其§S诉求§!的性质会随着状况发生改变，但记住§S人口§!的§S幸福度§!会受到其所属§S派系§!的§S赞同度§!影响。\n\n我们也可以用§S管理派系§!来调整某个§S派系§!与国家之间的关系，甚至接纳某个强大§S派系§!的思潮。"
NEW TUTORIAL_CREATESECTOR_DESC:1 "In §SSector Management Mode§!, planets are added to new or existing §SSectors§! on a per-system basis, for a slight £influence£ §SInfluence§! cost.\n\n§SSectors§! automate the construction of planetary buildings, greatly reducing the need for micromanagement, and can be tasked with specific production focuses and assigned different tax rates."
OLD TUTORIAL_CREATESECTOR_DESC:1 "In §SSector Management Mode§!, planets are added to new or existing §SSectors§! on a per-system basis, for a slight £influence  §SInfluence§! cost.\n\n§SSectors§! automate the construction of planetary buildings, greatly reducing the need for micromanagement, and can be tasked with specific production focuses and assigned different tax rates."
CHANGE TUTORIAL_CREATESECTOR_DESC:1 "在§S星域管理模式§!中，把相邻的行星添加到新的或已有的§S星域§! ，按照每个星系的基准需要花费少量的£influence£ §S影响力§!。\n\n§S星域§!使行星建筑的建造实现自动化，极大减少微观管理。还可以按照具体的侧重点进行生产以及分配不同的税率。"
