NEW TUTORIAL_PLANETVIEW_EDICTS_DESC:3 "These are planet-specific §SDecisions§!, orders or practices that can be temporarily enforced by spending some of our resources.\n\nNew §SDecisions§! may become available as we research new technologies and encounter new situations."
OLD TUTORIAL_PLANETVIEW_EDICTS_DESC:1 "These are planet-specific §SEdicts§!, practices that can be temporarily enforced by spending some of our Influence.\n\nNew §SEdicts§! become available as we research new technologies and encounter new situations."
CN  TUTORIAL_PLANETVIEW_EDICTS_DESC:3 "这些是针对特定行星的§S法令§!，颁布需要耗费影响力，法令会在到期后失效。\n\n研究新科技，遭遇新状况均可解锁新的§S法令§!。"
CN2 TUTORIAL_PLANETVIEW_EDICTS_DESC:3 "这些是星球§S决策§!，即通过花费一些资源来实施的临时规定或命令，其效果只影响实施决策的星球。\n\n随着新科技的研发与遭遇新的状况，新的§S决策§!也会随之解锁。"
NEW TUTORIAL_OUTPOST_STATION_DESC:4 "This is our system's §SStarbase§!. These upgradable stations mark star system ownership and are most often tasked with producing all types of ships.\n\nThey can be specialized into a variety of functions through §SModules§! and §SBuildings§!, and they tend to be the last line of defense against enemy fleets in a system. We expand our borders by building §SStarbases§! in nearby systems, and enemy §SStarbases§! can be captured by attacking them.\n\nOnce we have colonized more planets, we can manage our §STrade Routes§! via the §SStarbase§! interface as well."
OLD TUTORIAL_OUTPOST_STATION_DESC:3 "This is our system's §SStarbase§!. These massive space stations are the last line of defense in a system, and they are also used to produce military ships.\n\nEach system can only support a single Starbase. Building one in an uninhabited system will give us ownership of it. In the future, technologies may be unlocked that lets us upgrade Starbases further, allowing them to house an even greater number of §SModules§! and §SBuildings§!."
CN  TUTORIAL_OUTPOST_STATION_DESC:4 "这个是我们星系的§S太空基地§!。这些巨大的空间站是我们星系的最后防线，它们也可以用来制造军舰。\n\n每个星系只能支撑一个太空基地。在无人控制的星系中建造它，我们就能获得星系的所有权。在未来解锁的科技可能让我们能进一步升级太空基地，让它们能容纳更多的§S模块§!和§S建筑§!。"
CN2 TUTORIAL_OUTPOST_STATION_DESC:4 "这是我们星系的§S太空基地§!。这些可升级的空间站象征着星系的所有权，并且通常负责生产各种舰船。\n\n太空基地可以通过各种§S模块§!和§S建筑§!进行功能特化，并且通常也是星系抵御敌方舰队的最后一道防线。我们通过在临近星系中建造§S太空基地§!来拓展疆界，也可以通过攻击来占领敌方§S太空基地§!。\n\n等我们殖民更多星球之后，也可以在§S太空基地§!界面中管理§S贸易路线§!。"
NEW TUTORIAL_TRADITIONS_DESC:0 "The §HTraditions§! screen displays the §STradition trees§! available to our empire. A §STradition tree§! must first be §SAdopted§! before any §STraditions§! within it can be unlocked.\n\n§SAdopting§! a §STradition tree§! or unlocking a specific §STradition§! costs a certain amount of £unity£ §HUnity§! - and the price goes up as we unlock §STraditions§! and our empire grows."
OLD TUTORIAL_TRADITIONS_DESC:0 "The §HTraditions§! screen displays the §STradition trees§! available to our empire. A §STradition tree§! must first be §SAdopted§! before any §STraditions§! within it can be unlocked.\n\n§SAdopting§! a §STradition tree§! or unlocking a specific §STradition§! costs a certain amount of £unity  §HUnity§! - and the price goes up as we unlock §STraditions§! and our empire grows."
CHANGE TUTORIAL_TRADITIONS_DESC:0 "§H传统§!界面展示了我帝国能使用的§S传统树§!。解锁一个§S传统§!之前，必须先§S采用§!所属的§S传统树§!。\n\n§S采用§! §S传统树§! 或者解锁 §S传统§! 都需要花费 £unity£  §H凝聚力§! —— 并且随着帝国发展，解锁§S传统§!所需的点数也会增加。"
