NEW tutorial.1.desc:2 "Building a star empire can be a daunting task. To help get things started, I will be providing instructional missions that cover the basic steps necessary to establish ourselves as a successful interstellar power.\n\nThe first mission is to fully survey a neighboring star system. I have added it as an entry to the §SSituation Log§!. To access it, click on the Situation Log button in the left section of the top bar or press §SF2§!."
OLD tutorial.1.desc:2 "Building a star empire can be a daunting task. To help get things started, I will be providing instructional missions that cover the basic steps necessary to establish ourselves as a successful interstellar power.\n\nThe first mission is to fully survey a neighboring star system. I have added it as an entry to the §SSituation Log§!. To access it, click on the Situation Log button in the left section of the top bar or press §SF3§!."
CN  tutorial.1.desc:2 "建造恒星帝国或许看起来不是一件易事。为了保证你早日走上正轨，就由我来提供一系列指导任务，顺便简单介绍一下如何成功地建造庞大的跨星系势力。\n\n第一个任务是完成对一个相邻星系的全面勘察。我已经将任务作为一项添加到§S情报日志§!中。要查看他，请点击顶部栏目左边的情报日志按钮或者直接使用键盘§SF3§!键。"
CN2 tutorial.1.desc:2 "建设星际帝国绝非易事。为了保证您早日走上正轨，我将为您提供一系列教学任务，帮助您了解使我们成为一个成功的星际帝国所需的步骤。第一个任务是完全勘探我们的母星系。我已将其列入§S情报日志§!。您可点击顶部界面左端的情报日志按钮，或按下§SF3§!键来查看它。"
NEW tutorial.7.desc:1 "The resources generated by our homeworld will only take us so far. Our industry needs to expand off-world, and that requires a §SConstruction Ship§!.\n\nWe should build one as soon as we have amassed enough §SAlloys§! to do so."
OLD tutorial.7.desc:0 "The resources generated by our homeworld will only take us so far. Our industry needs to expand off-world, and that requires a §SConstruction Ship§!.\n\nWe should build one as soon as we have amassed enough §SMinerals§! to do so."
CN  tutorial.7.desc:1 "母星上生产的资源只够我们暂时使用，我们的工业需要向外拓展，这就需要§S工程船§!。\n\n一旦收集了足够的§S矿物§!，就立即建造吧。"
CN2 tutorial.7.desc:1 "母星上生产的资源只够我们暂时使用，我们的工业需要向外拓展，这就需要§S工程船§!。\n\n一旦收集了足够的§S矿物§!，就立即建造吧。"
NEW tutorial.9.desc:1 "The resources generated by our homeworld will only take us so far. Luckily our §SScience Ship§! has just found a resource deposit on another world! The time has come to use our §SConstruction Ship§! to build a §SMining Station§!.\n\nMining Stations can be built within our borders and automatically collect §SMinerals§! and any §SStrategic Resources§! found on the bodies they orbit. Keep in mind that they have an £energy£ §SEnergy Credit§! upkeep cost."
OLD tutorial.9.desc:1 "The resources generated by our homeworld will only take us so far. Luckily our §SScience Ship§! has just found a resource deposit on another world! The time has come to use our §SConstruction Ship§! to build a §SMining Station§!.\n\nMining Stations can be built within our borders and automatically collect §SMinerals§! and any §SStrategic Resources§! found on the bodies they orbit. Keep in mind that they have an £energy  §SEnergy Credit§! upkeep cost."
CHANGE tutorial.9.desc:1 "母星上生产的资源只够我们暂时使用，好在我们的§S科研船§!发现了一处资源矿藏！是时候用§S工程船§!建造一个§S采矿基地§!了。\n\n采矿基地可以在帝国境内建造，可自动采集其轨道天体上的§S矿物§!和§S战略资源§!。记住，它们需要£energy£ §S能源点数§!进行维护。"
NEW tutorial.11.desc:0 "Surveyed worlds sometimes possess unique properties that make them valuable objects of research. These £physics£ §SPhysics§!, £society£ §SSociety§! or £engineering£ §SEngineering§! resources can be collected by a §SResearch Station§!. My programming strongly compels me to compel you to build one.\n\nKeep in mind that §SResearch Stations§! can only be built within our borders, and have a upkeep cost in £energy£ §SEnergy Credits§!."
OLD tutorial.11.desc:0 "Surveyed worlds sometimes possess unique properties that make them valuable objects of research. These £physics  §SPhysics§!, £society  §SSociety§! or £engineering  §SEngineering§! resources can be collected by a §SResearch Station§!. My programming strongly compels me to compel you to build one.\n\nKeep in mind that §SResearch Stations§! can only be built within our borders, and have a upkeep cost in £energy  §SEnergy Credits§!."
CHANGE tutorial.11.desc:0 "勘察过的星球有些会具有特殊性质，是非常好的研究项目。这些£physics£ §S物理§!，£society£ §S社会§!和£engineering£ §S工程§!资源可以用§S科研基地§!采集。我的程序强烈建议我强烈建议你建造一个科研基地。\n\n记住§S科研基地§!只能在帝国境内建造，它们需要£energy£ §S能源点数§!的维持费用。"
NEW tutorial.13.name:1 "Tutorial: Planetary Districts and Buildings"
OLD tutorial.13.name:0 "Tutorial: Planetary Buildings"
CHANGE tutorial.13.name:1 "教程：行星地区和建筑"
CN2 tutorial.13.name:1 "教程：星球区划与建筑"
NEW tutorial.13.desc:4 "As an astute observer may already have noticed, habitable planets are divided into a number of §SDistricts§! and have multiple §SBuilding Slots§!. Districts provide §SJobs§! which produce basic resources, while §SPlanetary Buildings§! provide jobs which produce services or refined resources.\n\nOur homeworld already has several districts and a few buildings, including our capital, but the time has come to add more. §SPops§! who do not have a job are considered to be §SUnemployed§!.\n\nMore building slots will be unlocked as the number of Pops increases."
OLD tutorial.13.desc:2 "As an astute observer may already have noticed, habitable planets are divided into a number of §SSurface Tiles§!. Tiles can generate resources, but we will need §SPlanetary Buildings§! to get the most out of them.\n\nOur homeworld already has a few buildings, including our capital, but the time has come to add more. §SPops§! who are not working a resource or staffing a §SBuilding§! on a §STile§! are considered to be §SUnemployed§!."
CHANGE tutorial.13.desc:4 "观察敏锐的人可能已经发现了，可居住的行星分为数个§S地区§!，同时有多个§S建筑槽位§!。地区提供生产基础资源的§S职位§!，而§S行星建筑§!则提供服务职位或精炼资源的职位。\n\n我们的母星上已经有数个地区和少量建筑了，包括我们的都城，不过是时候再添几个了。没有工作的§S人口§!被视作§S失业§!状态。\n\n建筑槽位会随着人口数量的增长逐渐解锁。"
CN2 tutorial.13.desc:4 "观察敏锐的人可能已经发现了，可居住的星球分为数个§S区划§!，并且有多个§S建筑槽位§!。区划提供生产基础资源的§S职位§!，而§S星球建筑§!则提供服务职位或精炼资源的职位。\n\n我们的母星上已经有了一些区划和建筑，包括我们的首都，但现在该增添一些了。没有职位的§S人口§!会成为§S失业§!状态。\n\n建筑槽位会随着人口数量的增长逐渐解锁。"
NEW tutorial.15.name:1 "Tutorial: Blocked Features"
OLD tutorial.15.name:0 "Tutorial: Tile Blockers"
CN  tutorial.15.name:1 "教程：地块障碍"
CN2 tutorial.15.name:1 "教程：障碍特征"
NEW tutorial.15.desc:1 "§SPlanetary Features§! on habitable planets are sometimes blocked, preventing their exploitation. Clearing a £blocker£ §SBlocked Feature§! takes time and costs £minerals£ §SMinerals§! or £energy£ §SEnergy Credits§!, but the free space often makes it worthwhile.\n\nMany blocked features require specific technologies before they can be removed, but the ones on our homeworld can be dealt with as soon as we have the credits to spare."
OLD tutorial.15.desc:0 "§SSurface Tiles§! on habitable planets are sometimes blocked, preventing their use. Clearing a £blocker  §STile Blocker§! takes time and costs £minerals  §SMinerals§! and £energy  §SEnergy Credits§!, but the free space often makes it worthwhile.\n\nMany tile blockers require specific technologies before they can be removed, but the ones on our homeworld can be dealt with as soon as we have the credits to spare."
CN  tutorial.15.desc:1 "可居住行星上的§S表面地块§!有时会有障碍存在，无法使用。清除一个£blocker §S地形障碍§!要消耗£minerals §S矿物§!和£energy §S能源点数§!，但空出来的地块肯定物超所值。\n\n许多地形障碍需要特定的科技才能进行移除，但母星上的这些只要拥有足够点数就可以了。"
CN2 tutorial.15.desc:1 "可居住星球上的§S星球特征§!有时处于障碍状态，无法得到利用。清理£blocker£ §S障碍特征§!需要花费时间和£minerals£ §S矿物§!或者£energy£ §S能源点数§!，但腾出来的空间通常使其物有所值。\n\n许多障碍特征都需要特定的科技才能清理，但我们母星上的那些只要有足够的能源点数即可。"
NEW tutorial.16.desc:1 "Yet another impediment to our galactic ambitions has been dealt with. That §SBlocked Feature§! is now ready to be exploited!"
OLD tutorial.16.desc:0 "Yet another impediment to our galactic ambitions has been dealt with. That §STile Blocker§! never stood a chance!"
CN  tutorial.16.desc:1 "又一个征服星辰大海的障碍被消除了。那个§S地块障碍§!真是完败啊！"
CN2 tutorial.16.desc:1 "又一个阻碍我们征服星辰大海的障碍被铲除了。那块§S障碍特征§!现在已经可以开发了！"
NEW tutorial.33.desc:3 "A healthy supply of §SMinerals§!, §SAlloys§! and §SEnergy Credits§! is critical to the well-being of any interstellar power. We should take steps to increase our production of these resources.\n\nStations and Buildings cost Alloys or Minerals to build and Energy Credits to maintain. The same is true for Ships, except that they have an Alloy upkeep cost as well. These resources are produced by §SMining Stations§! or §SPlanetary Buildings§!. \n\nLater you may discover new and interesting resources to spend on esoteric new production."
OLD tutorial.33.desc:1 "A healthy supply of §SMinerals§! and §SEnergy Credits§! is critical to the well-being of any interstellar power. We should take steps to increase our production of these resources.\n\nStations and Buildings cost Minerals to build and Energy Credits to maintain. The same is true for Ships, except that they have a Mineral upkeep cost as well. Both resources are produced by §SMining Stations§! or §SPlanetary Buildings§!."
CN  tutorial.33.desc:3 "充足的 §S矿物§! 资源与 §S能源点数§! 对于每个星际势力来说都是至关重要的。我们应该增加这些资源的生产。\n\n空间站和建筑都会花费矿物资源来建造，并需要能源点数维持他们的运行。飞船也是如此，而且飞船还需要花费矿物来维持。这两种资源都可以通过 §S采矿基地§! 或者 §S行星建筑§!获得。"
CN2 tutorial.33.desc:3 "稳定的§S矿物§!、§S合金§!与§S能源点数§!供应是任何星际势力繁荣发展的关键。我们应当采取措施增加这些资源的产量。\n\n空间站和建筑需要消耗合金或矿物来建造，以及能源点数来维护。舰船也是如此，只不过它们也需要合金来维护。这些资源由§S开采站§!或§S星球建筑§!生产。\n\n后期你会发现一些有趣的新资源，可用于神秘的新建造。"
NEW tutorial.45.desc:1 "As our empire grows, new colonies will automatically be organized into §SSectors§!. Sectors can be managed from the §SPlanets and Sectors§! screen to automatically build and upgrade Districts and Buildings using assigned pools of Minerals and Energy."
OLD tutorial.45.desc:0 "Good work. This new §SSector§! should take a load off our backs and let us focus on more important matters.\n\nAs you colonize new planets, don't forget to add their systems to existing or new sectors to stay below the control limit."
CHANGE tutorial.45.desc:1 "随着帝国的发展，新殖民地将自动组成§S星域§!。星域可以在§S行星和星域§!界面进行管理，设置利用分配的矿物和能源点数，自动建造并升级地区和建筑。"
CN2 tutorial.45.desc:1 "随着帝国的发展，星球将自动组成§S星域§!。星域可以在§S星球与星域§!界面进行管理，并设置利用分配的矿物与能源点数，自动对区划与建筑进行建造与升级。"
NEW tutorial.46.desc:1 "§SGovernors§! can be assigned to administrate entire §SSectors§!. All planets within the sector will then benefit from the Governor's skills. We should assign one to our new sector."
OLD tutorial.46.desc:0 "§SGovernors§! can be assigned to administrate entire §SSectors§!, much in the same way as they rule individual colonies.\n\nAll planets within the sector will then benefit from the Governor's effects. We should assign one to our new sector."
CN  tutorial.46.desc:1 "§S星域§!可以通过部署§S总督§!进行管理，管理方式与管理单独的殖民星球大致相同。\n\n所有处于星域内的星球都将受到总督的影响而获得增益。请为我们的新星域部署一名新的总督。\n\n"
CN2 tutorial.46.desc:1 "你可以指派§S总督§!管理整个§S星域§!。星域内的所有星球都将从总督的技能中受益。我们应当为我们的新星域指派一位总督。"
NEW tutorial.55.desc:5 "We have uncovered a §SStrategic Resource§!! Many §SStrategic Resources§! require specific technologies to exploit, but can confer powerful bonuses.\n\nDon't forget to build §SStarbases§! where appropriate to secure the resources within our borders. Strategic Resources can be used to build advanced Buildings and Ship components or simply sold."
OLD tutorial.55.desc:4 "We have uncovered a §SStrategic Resource§!! Many §SStrategic Resources§! require specific technologies to exploit, but can confer powerful bonuses.\n\nDon't forget to build §SStarbases§! where appropriate to secure the resources within our borders. The effects of Strategic Resources do not stack, but controlling more than one source lets us trade the resource to another empire."
CN  tutorial.55.desc:5 "我们找到了一处§S战略资源§!！很多§S战略资源§!需要特定的科技才能开发，但能够得到强大的奖励。\n\n不要忘记建造§S太空基地§!保证这些资源位于我们境内。战略资源的作用不会叠加，但是控制多个来源可以将资源用于与其他帝国的交易中。"
CN2 tutorial.55.desc:5 "我们发现了一种§S战略资源§!！许多§S战略资源§!需要特定的科技才能利用，但可以从中获得强力的加成。\n\n别忘了在合适的地点建造§S太空基地§!来确保我们境内的资源。战略资源可以用来建造先进的建筑和舰船部件，或者干脆卖掉。"
NEW tutorial_3_chain_desc:2 "We will need a §SConstruction Ship§! if we are to exploit the resources that are discovered by our §SScience Ship§!.\n\nClick on our Starbase and select the §SShipyard§! tab, then select §SConstruction Ship§! from among the available choices.\n\nNote that you will need to have amassed enough §SAlloys§! to afford the ship before its construction can begin."
OLD tutorial_3_chain_desc:1 "We will need a §SConstruction Ship§! if we are to exploit the resources that are discovered by our §SScience Ship§!.\n\nCivilian ships like §SScience Ships§! do not require a §SStarbase§! and can be built planetside. Click on [Root.Capital.GetName] and select the §SSpaceport§! tab. Then click on the §SBuild§! button, and select §SConstruction Ship§! from among the available choices.\n\nNote that you will need to have amassed enough §SMinerals§! to afford the ship before its construction can begin."
CN  tutorial_3_chain_desc:2 "如果要开采 §S科研船§!发现的资源，就需要一艘 §S工程船§!。\n\像§S工程船§!这样的民用船只不需要§S太空基地§!，由行星直接建造。点击[Root.Capital.GetName]并选择§S太空港§!标签。然后点击§S建造§!按钮，并从可选项中选择§S工程船§!。\n\n注意，需要有足够的§S矿物§!才能建造工程船。"
CN2 tutorial_3_chain_desc:2 "如果要开采§S科研船§!发现的资源，就需要一艘§S工程船§!。\n\n要建造一艘工程船，需要进入[Root.Capital.GetName]轨道上的§S太空港§!。直接点击或者在母星星球界面选择太空港标签，然后点击§S建造§!按钮，选择§S工程船§!。\n\n注意，需要有足够的§S矿物§!才能建造工程船。"
NEW tutorial_6_chain_desc:1 "Each population unit, or §SPop§!, in our empire works in a §SJob§! on a planet. Jobs are created by §SBuildings§! or §SDistricts§!.\n\nOur homeworld already has a small number of districts, but we should construct more. Build an §SAgriculture District§!, a §SMining District§!, or a §SGenerator District§!.\n\nTo do this, click on our homeworld and go into its §SPlanet Summary§! tab. Then click the relevant district type and click on the §SBuild§! button. Make your choice from among the available options, and, assuming we have enough §SMinerals§!, construction will begin on the new district. Don't forget, the district only makes a job available, nothing will be produced without a pop working there. You can see which jobs your pops are working in on the §SPopulation§! tab."
OLD tutorial_6_chain_desc:0 "Each population unit, or §SPop§!, in our empire works a §SSurface Tile§! on a planet. Some tiles possess a small amount of resources by default, but §SPlanetary Buildings§! are needed to get the most out of our planets and population.\n\nOur homeworld already has a small number of buildings, but we should construct another. Build a §SHydroponics Farm§!, a §SMining Network§!, a §SPower Plant§! or a §SBasic Science Lab§! in an available tile.\n\nTo do this, click on our homeworld and go into its §SSurface§! tab. Then select an empty tile and click on the §SBuild§! button. Select your choice from among the available options, and, assuming we have enough §SMinerals§!, construction will begin on the new building. Don't forget to assign a Pop to the building when it has been finished."
CHANGE tutorial_6_chain_desc:1 "我帝国的每个§S人口§!都要在行星上的某个§S职位§!工作。职位由§S建筑§!和§S地区§!创造。\n\n我们的母星已经有了数个地区，但我们应该多建几个。建造一个§S农业区§!、§S矿业区§!或§S电力区§!。\n\n为此，点击母星，进入§S行星总览§!标签页。然后点击相应的地区类型，点击§S建造§!按钮。做出你自己的选择，如果拥有足够的§S矿物§!，新地区的建设将会开始。建筑完成之后请不要忘记部署人口。不要忘记，每个地区只提供一个职位。如果没有人口工作，就不会有任何产出。您可以在§S人口§!标签页查看您的人口正在什么职位上工作。"
CN2 tutorial_6_chain_desc:1 "我们帝国的每个§S人口§!都要在行星的§S地表地块§!上工作。某些地块会默认包含一些资源，但想要增加星球的利用效率与人口上限，则需要建造§S行星建筑§!。\n\n我们的母星已经拥有一些建筑，但还需要继续进行建造。在可用地块上建造一个§S水培农场§!，§S复合矿场§!，§S发电站§!，或者§S基础科学研究所§!。\n\n为此，需要点击母星，进入§S地表§!标签页，然后选择任意一块地块，点击§S建造§!按钮。选择你要的建筑。若拥有足够的§S矿物§!，则会开始建造。建筑完成之后请不要忘记安排人口。"
NEW tutorial_7_chain_title:1 "Tutorial: Blocked Features"
OLD tutorial_7_chain_title:0 "Tutorial: Tile Blockers"
CN  tutorial_7_chain_title:1 "教程：地块障碍"
CN2 tutorial_7_chain_title:1 "教程：障碍特征"
NEW tutorial_7_chain_desc:1 "Several of the §SPlanetary Features§! on our homeworld are blocked and cannot be used. One of our priorities should be to clear them out, making the Features available for §SDistricts§! to be built there. This takes time and costs §SEnergy Credits§!, so it will have to be done gradually.\n\nTo clear a §SPlanetary Feature§!, click the §SShow Planetary Features§! button in our homeworld's planet interface. Select a blocked feature and then click on the §SClear blocker§! button. The process of clearing the feature will now begin, assuming you can afford it.\n\nNote that different feature blockers have different costs and times associated with clearing them. §SGovernors§! can also have an effect on this."
OLD tutorial_7_chain_desc:0 "Several of the §SSurface Tiles§! on our homeworld are blocked and cannot be used. One of our first priorities should be to clear them out, making the tiles available for §SPops§! and §SBuildings§!. This takes time and costs §SEnergy Credits§!, so it will have to be done gradually.\n\nTo clear a §STile Blocker§!, go into the §SSurface§! tab in our homeworld's planet interface. Select a blocked tile and then click on the §SClear§! button. The process of clearing the tile will now begin, assuming you can afford it.\n\nNote that different Tile Blockers have different costs and times associated with clearing them. §SPlanetary Governors§! can also have an effect on this."
CHANGE tutorial_7_chain_desc:1 "我们母星上的一些§S行星地貌§!被障碍阻住，无法使用。我们的优先事项之一就是对它们进行清理，以便在这些地貌上建设§S地区§!。这一过程需要时间并会消耗§S能源点数§!，所以要慢慢来。\n\n为了清理§S行星地貌§!，在母星的行星界面点击§S显示行星地貌§!按钮。选择一个被障碍阻住的地貌，然后点击§S清理障碍§!按钮。只要你付得起费用，清理地貌的工作就会立刻开始。\n\n注意，清理不同地貌障碍需要的时间和资源量也不同。§S总督§!也会对此产生影响。"
CN2 tutorial_7_chain_desc:1 "我们母星上的一些§S星球特征§!是无法利用的障碍。我们的优先事项之一就是清理这些特征，把空间腾出来建造§S区划§!。这需要花费时间和§S能源点数§!，所以必须一步一步来。\n\n要清理§S星球特征§!，先点击母星界面上的§S星球特征§!按钮，选择一个障碍特征，然后点击§S清理障碍§!按钮。只要你付得起花费，清理特征的工作就将开始。\n\n请注意，清理不同的障碍特征需要的花费和时间也有所不同。§S总督§!可能也会带来影响。"
