NEW tutorial_9_chain_desc:3 "We should consider building a second §SScience Ship§! to increase the speed at which we survey our region of the galaxy.\n\nClick on our Starbase and select the §SShipyard§! tab, then select §SScience Ship§! from among the available choices.\n\nNote that you will need to have amassed enough §SAlloys§! to afford the ship before its construction can begin."
OLD tutorial_9_chain_desc:2 "We should consider building a second §SScience Ship§! to increase the speed at which we survey our region of the galaxy.\n\nCivilian ships like §SScience Ships§! do not require a §SStarbase§! and can be built planetside. Click on [Root.Capital.GetName] and select the §SSpaceport§! tab. Then click on the §SBuild§! button, and select §SScience Ship§! from among the available choices.\n\nNote that you will need to have amassed enough §SMinerals§! to afford the ship before its construction can begin."
CN  tutorial_9_chain_desc:3 "我们应该考虑建造第二艘 §S科研船§!，以便增加我们探索宇宙的速度。\n\n像§S科研船§!这样的民用船只不需要§S太空基地§!，由行星直接建造。点击[Root.Capital.GetName]并选择§S太空港§!标签。然后点击§S建造§!按钮，并从可选项中选择§S科研船§!。\n\n注意，需要有足够的§S矿物§!才能建造工程船。"
CN2 tutorial_9_chain_desc:3 "我们应该考虑建造第二艘§S科研船§!，以便增加我们探索宇宙的速度。\n\n要进行建造，请进入母星轨道上的§S太空港§!。你可以直接点击太空港或者在母星界面上选择太空港标签，然后点击§S建造§!按钮并选择§S科研船§!。"
NEW tutorial_11_chain_desc:4 "The time has come to colonize another world. First we will have to build a §SColony Ship§!. These ships take a long time to build and require a large amount of §SAlloys§!, §SFood§!, and §SConsumer Goods§!, but a thriving colony will more than return on this investment.\n\nClick on your Starbase and select the §SShipyard§! tab. Then click on the §SBuild Ship§! button, and select §SColony Ship§! from among the available choices.\n\nNote that you will need to have amassed enough resources to afford the ship before its construction can begin."
OLD tutorial_11_chain_desc:2 "The time has come to colonize another world. First we will have to build a §SColony Ship§!. These ships take a long time to build and require a large amount of §SMinerals§!, but a thriving colony will more than return on this investment.\n\nCivilian ships like §SColony Ships§! do not require a §SStarbase§! and can be built planetside. Click on [Root.Capital.GetName] and select the §SSpaceport§! tab. Then click on the §SBuild§! button, and select §SColony Ship§! from among the available choices.\n\nNote that you will need to have amassed enough §SMinerals§! to afford the ship before its construction can begin."
CN  tutorial_11_chain_desc:4 "是时候去殖民下一个星球了。首先我们要建造一艘§S殖民船§!。这些飞船将会耗费大量时间和§S矿物§!，但是建立的殖民地发达后就能得到比投资多得多的回报。\n\n像§S殖民船§!这样的民用船只不需要§S太空基地§!，由行星直接建造。点击[Root.Capital.GetName]并选择§S太空港§!标签。然后点击§S建造§!按钮，并从可选项中选择§S殖民船§!。\n\n请注意，你需要在开始前为建造飞船积累足够的§S矿物§!。"
CN2 tutorial_11_chain_desc:4 "现在该殖民另一颗星球了。首先我们得建造一艘§S殖民船§!。建造这些殖民船需要花很长时间，以及大量的§S合金§!、§S食物§!和§S消费品§!，但兴旺发展的殖民地带来的回报远远大于这笔投入。\n\n点击你的太空基地，并选择§S船坞§!界面。然后点击§S建造舰船§!按钮，并选择§S殖民船§!。\n\n请注意，在建造开始之前，你必须先积累足够的资源。"
NEW tutorial_12_chain_desc:3 "We should now use our new §SColony Ship§! to establish our first colony. The best planetary candidates are those that are of the same planet class as our homeworld - our colonists will have no problems adjusting to their environments.\n\nTo colonize a planet, click on your Colony Ship or select it in the §SOutliner§!. Then click on the §SColonize§! button in its fleet interface, and select the planet you want to colonize. Note that you can only colonize planets that have been surveyed and have no §SAnomalies§!. They must also be located within your borders. While you can choose to colonize low Habitability planets, doing so can be very expensive."
OLD tutorial_12_chain_desc:1 "We should now use our new §SColony Ship§! to establish our first colony. The best planetary candidates are those that are of the same planet class as our homeworld - our colonists will have no problems adjusting to their environments.\n\nTo colonize a planet, click on your Colony Ship or select it in the §SOutliner§!. Then click on the §SColonize§! button in its fleet interface, and select the planet you want to colonize. Note that you can only colonize planets that have been surveyed, that have no §SAnomalies§! and that you have researched the necessary technology for. They must also be located within your borders.\n\nWhen you have selected an appropriate planet, you will be prompted to place your first colony building on a tile. As soon as you have done this, your Colony Ship will blast off to establish our new colony."
CN  tutorial_12_chain_desc:3 "接下来，就该使用新造的§S殖民船§!建立我们的第一个殖民地了。最佳的殖民星球应该是和我们母星环境差不多的星球，这样殖民者就不会有适应环境的问题。\n\n要对星球进行殖民，点击你的殖民船或者在§S信息缩略表§!选择飞船，然后在飞船的船队界面点击§S殖民§!按钮，选择想要殖民的星球。注意，你只能对已勘察过，没有§S异常现象§!，并已研究相关科技的星球进行殖民。它们也位于你的边境线之内。\n\n选择一个合适的星球后，则要选择放置第一个殖民建筑的地块。完成这些后，你的殖民船就会马上开始建立新的殖民地。"
CN2 tutorial_12_chain_desc:3 "现在我们该用新造的§S殖民船§!来设立我们的第一个殖民地。最佳的候选星球是与我们的母星类型相同的星球，这样我们的殖民者在适应环境方面不会有任何问题。\n\n要殖民一颗星球，点击你的殖民船，或者在§S概览窗口§!中选中它。然后在其舰队界面中点击§S殖民§!按钮，并选择你想殖民的星球。注意你只能在已勘测并且没有§S异常§!的星球上殖民。星球也必须位于你的境内。虽然你可以选择在宜居性较低的星球上殖民，但代价会非常高昂。"
NEW tutorial_14_chain_desc:1 "Continue to expand our empire by founding new colonies. Build more §SColony Ships§! when we have enough §SAlloys§!, §SFood§!, and §SConsumer Goods§! then send them off to establish new colonies.\n\nTake care not to have too many colonies under development at the same time, since they drain §SEnergy Credits§! until they become self-sufficient."
OLD tutorial_14_chain_desc:0 "Continue to expand our empire by founding new colonies. Build more §SColony Ships§! when we have enough §SMinerals§!, and send them off to establish new colonies.\n\nTake care not to have too many colonies under development at the same time, since they drain §SEnergy Credits§! until they become self-sufficient."
CN  tutorial_14_chain_desc:1 "继续通过建立更多的殖民地扩展我们的帝国。收集足够§S矿物§!后，建造更多的§S殖民船§!，完成后便将他们派去建立新的殖民地吧。\n\n注意不要同时发展太多殖民地，因为殖民地在达成自给自足状态前会消耗大量§S能源点数§!。"
CN2 tutorial_14_chain_desc:1 "继续通过建立更多的殖民地扩张我们的帝国。收集足够§S矿物§!后，建造更多的§S殖民船§!，完成后便将他们派去建立新的殖民地吧。\n\n注意不要同时发展太多殖民地，因为殖民地在达成自给自足状态前会消耗大量§S能源§!。"
NEW tutorial_15_chain_desc:1 "Our growing industry is ravenous for raw materials, and we need to increase our supply of §SMinerals§!. This is done by building §SMining Stations§! above planets and asteroids with Mineral deposits, or by building §SMining Districts§! on the surface of one of our inhabited planets.\n\nAs both stations and buildings cost §SEnergy Credits§! to maintain, we need to establish an ample supply of this resource as well. Energy Credits are produced by §SGenerator Districts§! on the surface of our inhabited planets. They can also be acquired by §SMining Stations§! built over planets, asteroids or suns with Energy Credit deposits."
OLD tutorial_15_chain_desc:0 "Our growing industry is ravenous for raw materials, and we need to increase our supply of §SMinerals§!. This is done by building §SMining Stations§! above planets and asteroids with Mineral deposits, or by building §SMining Networks§! on the surface of one of our inhabited planets.\n\nAs both stations and buildings cost §SEnergy Credits§! to maintain, we need to establish an ample supply of this resource as well. Energy Credits are produced by §SPower Plants§! on the surface of our inhabited planets. They can also be acquired by §SMining Stations§! built over planets, asteroids or suns with Energy Credit deposits."
CHANGE tutorial_15_chain_desc:1 "我们持续发展的工业渴求原料，必须增加我们的§S矿物§!供应。在拥有矿物矿藏的行星或小行星上建立§S采矿基地§!，或在已殖民行星的表面上建设§S矿业区§!即可获得矿物。\n\n由于所有基地和建筑都会消耗§S能源点数§!维持运转，我们也需要增加能源点数的收入。能源点数可以在已殖民行星表面上的§S电力区§!生产，也可以通过§S采矿基地§!从具有能源点数矿藏的行星、小行星或恒星获得。"
CN2 tutorial_15_chain_desc:1 "我们不断成长的工业渴求原料，因此必须增加§S矿物§!的产量。我们可以在有矿物储藏的星球和小行星上建造§S开采站§!，或是在某个已殖民的星球表面上建造§S采矿区划§!。\n\n空间站和建筑都需要§S能源点数§!来维护，因此我们也需要保证这项资源的充足供应。能源点数由已殖民星球上的§S发电区划§!生产，也可以通过在有能源点数储藏的星球、小行星和恒星上建造§S开采站§!来生产。"
NEW tutorial_16_chain_desc:4 "We must build up a potent starfleet to ensure the security of the [Root.GetName].\n\nWith the resources now at our disposal, we shouldn't have any problems building at least five more §SCorvettes§!. Build the ships at a §SStarbase§! when our §SAlloy§! supplies permit. New military ships always join any existing fleets that orbit the star of the §SStarbase§! that builds them.\n\nAlso be sure to recruit and assign an §SAdmiral§! to our new fleet. This works in the same way as assigning §SScientists§! to a §SScience Ship§! - click on the §SAssign Leader§! box in the fleet interface, and recruit a new Admiral from there. A skilled Admiral commanding a fleet can increase its performance dramatically."
OLD tutorial_16_chain_desc:2 "We must build up a potent starfleet to ensure the security of the [Root.GetName].\n\nWith the resources now at our disposal, we shouldn't have any problems building at least five more §SCorvettes§!. Build the ships at a §SStarbase§! when our §SMineral§! supplies permit. New military ships always join any existing fleets that orbit the star of the §SStarbase§! that builds them.\n\nAlso be sure to recruit and assign an §SAdmiral§! to our new fleet. This works in the same way as assigning §SScientists§! to a §SScience Ship§! - click on the §SAssign Leader§! box in the fleet interface, and recruit a new Admiral from there. A skilled Admiral commanding a fleet can increase its performance dramatically."
CN  tutorial_16_chain_desc:4 "我们必须打造一支强有力的星际舰队，以保卫[Root.GetName]的安全。\n\n考虑到目前拥有的资源数量，再建造五艘§S护卫舰§!是绝不成问题的。在§S矿物§!补给允许的情况下，在§S太空基地§!建造船只。新建造的军舰都将自动加入生产该军舰的§S太空基地§!所在恒星轨道上的舰队。\n\n不要忘记为我们的新舰队指派一位§S舰队司令§!。这一过程与将§S科学家§!指派到§S科研船§!的过程并无两样——点击舰队界面的§S指派领袖§!，便可为舰队指派舰队司令。在经验丰富的舰队司令指挥下，舰队的战斗表现将有飞跃性的提升。"
CN2 tutorial_16_chain_desc:4 "我们必须组建一支强大的星际舰队，以确保[Root.GetName]的安全。\n\n有了这些资源，我们应该可以至少再建造五艘§S护卫舰§!。等我们的§S合金§!供应允许的时候，通过§S太空基地§!建造这些舰船。新造的军舰会加入§S太空基地§!所处的恒星轨道上已有的舰队。\n\n另外也要记得招募一位§S上将§!，并派遣到我们的新舰队。操作方式和派遣§S科学家§!到§S科研船§!一样，在舰队界面中点击§S派遣领袖§!框，并新招募一位上将。一位老练的上将可以大幅增强舰队的战斗力。"
NEW tutorial_18_chain_desc:1 "We should assign a §SGovernor§! to administrate our new §SSector§!. All planets within the sector will then benefit from the effects of the Governor's skill level and traits.\n\nTo do this, go into the §SPlanets and Sectors§! view by clicking on its associated icon in the top bar drop-down list or press §SF4§!. In the §SPlanets§! tab, scroll to the button to find our new sector. Click on the §SAssign Leader§! box, and assign a new or existing Governor from there."
OLD tutorial_18_chain_desc:1 "We should assign a §SGovernor§! to administrate our new §SSector§!. All planets within the sector will then benefit from the effects of the Governor's skill level and traits.\n\nTo do this, go into the §SPlanets and Sectors§! view by clicking on its associated icon in the top bar drop-down list or press §SF5§!. In the §SPlanets§! tab, scroll to the button to find our new sector. Click on the §SAssign Leader§! box, and assign a new or existing Governor from there."
CN  tutorial_18_chain_desc:1 "接下来要为新的§S星域§!指派一名§S总督§!。所有星域内的星球都能从该名总督的技能和特质中获得相应收益。\n\n要如此做，点击屏幕顶部的下拉菜单或者按下§SF5§!前往§S行星和星域§!界面。在§S星球§!标签下，选择我们的新星域。点击§S指派领袖§!框，然后指派一名新的总督或一名已经存在的总督。"
CN2 tutorial_18_chain_desc:1 "我们该指派一位§S总督§!来管理我们的新§S星域§!。星域中的所有行星将受益于总督的能力等级与特性。\n\n要指派一位总督，请点击屏幕顶部的下拉菜单，或是按下§SF5§!来进入§S行星和星域§!界面。在§S行星§!页面中，拖动至底部来找到我们的新星域。点击§S指派领袖§!框，并指派一位新的或已有的总督。"
NEW tutorial_19_chain_desc:2 "To create a new ship design, go into the §SShip Designer§! by clicking on its associated icon in the top bar's drop-down menu, or press §SF9§!. Click on the §SNew Design§! button, and select §SCorvette§! when you are prompted to select a §SHull Size§!. The next step is to pick a §SSection§! for the design by clicking on the §SNo Section§! button at the top of the window.\n\nCorvettes are the smallest type of warship, and they are made up of only a single section unlike larger vessels. Sections determine the amount of §SWeapon§! and §SUtility§! slots on a ship. Pick one, and then start filling up the available slots with components. Make sure that the components do not exceed the power output of the reactor - a ship's power supply cannot be in the negative.\n\nIf you want to make things easy, simply click on the §SAuto-complete Ship§! button and the game will finish the design for you."
OLD tutorial_19_chain_desc:2 "To create a new ship design, go into the §SShip Designer§! by clicking on its associated icon in the top bar's drop-down menu, or press §SF10§!. Click on the §SNew Design§! button, and select §SCorvette§! when you are prompted to select a §SHull Size§!. The next step is to pick a §SSection§! for the design by clicking on the §SNo Section§! button at the top of the window.\n\nCorvettes are the smallest type of warship, and they are made up of only a single section unlike larger vessels. Sections determine the amount of §SWeapon§! and §SUtility§! slots on a ship. Pick one, and then start filling up the available slots with components. Make sure that the components do not exceed the power output of the reactor - a ship's power supply cannot be in the negative.\n\nIf you want to make things easy, simply click on the §SAuto-complete Ship§! button and the game will finish the design for you."
CN  tutorial_19_chain_desc:2 "如果想要新建船只设计，点击屏幕顶部的下拉菜单或者按下§SF10§!键前往§S舰船设计器§!界面。点击§S新设计§!键，在出现选择§S船体尺寸§!时，选择§S护卫舰§!。下一步，点击窗口上方的§S未选区块§!按钮，以为新设计选择§S区块设计§!。\n\n护卫舰是体形最小的战舰，不像大型船只，只由单一模块构成。模块决定了船只的§S武器§!和§S设施§!栏位数量。选择一个栏位，并使用组件填充可用的栏位。请确保组件的耗能不要超出反应堆输出功率 —— 舰船的能源供应不能为负数。\n\n如果你怕麻烦，简单点一下 §S自动完成设计§! 按钮，系统帮你搞定设计方案。"
CN2 tutorial_19_chain_desc:2 "要设计一艘新船，请点击屏幕顶部的下拉菜单，或是按下§SF10§!来进入§S舰船设计§!界面。点击§S新设计§!按钮，然后在§S舰体尺寸§!中选择§S护卫舰§!。下一步将为该设计选择一个§S区块§!，请点击窗口顶部的§S无区块§!按钮。\n\n护卫舰是最小型的飞船，不像大型飞船，它们只有一个区块。区块决定了飞船上的§S武器§!与§S设施§!槽。选择一个区块，然后逐个为空余槽位选择部件。别忘了添加§S裂变反应堆§!——飞船的能源供应必须保持为正数。\n\n如果您觉得太麻烦，只需点击§S自动装配§!按钮，系统会自动帮您完成设计。"
